---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Services | NexGen Binary" active="services">

<main class="container page">
  <div class="section-head"><h1>Services</h1><p class="muted">Updated service icons and service coverage for dental and healthcare offices.</p></div>
  <div class="grid2">
    <article class="card"><div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-network-wired icon"></i></div><h3>Fully Managed IT</h3><p>Complete outsourced support for daily operations, maintenance, and user support.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-people-group icon"></i></div><h3>Co-Managed IT</h3><p>Support your internal IT team with escalation support and project assistance.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-cloud icon"></i></div><h3>Microsoft 365 & Cloud</h3><p>Tenant administration, email support, MFA support, and account assistance.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-virus icon"></i></div><h3>Security Support</h3><p>Endpoint protection support, backup checks, and risk-reduction guidance.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot icon"></i></div><h3>Local & Responsive Support</h3><p>Richmond-area service with remote triage and onsite assistance when needed.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-clipboard-check icon"></i></div><h3>Documentation & Standards</h3><p>Runbooks, asset notes, and support documentation for consistency.</p></article>
  </div>
  <div class="inline-row top-gap"><a href="/consultation#book" class="btn primary track" data-event="cta_click" data-label="services_book"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i> Book a Consult</a></div>
</main>

</Layout>
